            </p>
            <div id="c7f63e40-3e66-4ff2-9b52-8e8e3de1a5d0">
               <p>
                  <ph conkeyref="b_bp_mla/p_pnk_vdh_r4b"/>in authority records if used as a component of an authorized or variant access point. <ph conkeyref="b_bp_mla/ph_khy_xxc_gqb"/> in other cases if readily ascertainable. </p>
               <p>In bibliographic records: <ph conkeyref="b_bp_mla/ph_kph_pcz_x4b"/>
               </p>
