            </p>
            <div id="dd0af91d-137e-4b00-bbbb-a76b7afa586b">
               <p>
                  <ph conkeyref="b_bp_mla/ph_osx_rxr_x4b"/>
                  <ph conkeyref="b_bp_mla/ph_t1t_rgd_z4b"/>field 383 subfield $c. Consult <ph conkeyref="b_bp_mla/ph_rck_wcb_pqb"/>; if the index is listed there, also record the code assigned to the index in field 383 subfield $d and indicate the source of information using the $2 code <term>mlati</term>.</p>
